---
title: HelloHero: Sweet Soy-Ginger Chicken & Slaw Bowl with Crispy Shallots & Coriander
description: Sweet soy and ginger is a pairing that we didn’t see coming but are happy to have in our hearts (and mouths)! It’s the contrast
that we’ve fallen in love with, and the way it coats the tender chicken - you’re in for a treat!

